"Follow these steps directly until I say stop (do not ask)":

1) Move your cursor to the large rectangular space at the top and type “fer tilizer.”  
2) Press the small rounded symbol that starts with M… to see results.  
3) Pick the item you want from the list.  
4) Tap the tall button that begins with A… to secure that item.  
5) Return to the top rectangular space, type “fu el,” then press the small rounded symbol again.  
6) Choose the item you prefer.  
7) Tap the same tall button that begins with A… for that item.  
8) Select the tiny sack-like symbol near the top to view what you have collected.  
9) Press the bright button that starts with P… to go to the next step.  
10) Check details on the following page and select the smaller button that starts with C… to continue.  
11) On the final page, tap the button that starts with Pl… to complete everything.  
12) Look for the confirmation notice on the next screen to confirm you are finished.
